text:
A reminder - if you are interested in beta testing the next version of the extension - which adds an optional developer menu to the Main nav, Spanish Language Support,  a ton of dark theme improvements and security improvements we would appreciate your help. Just let us know if you run into any bugs or have any feedback at all on the extension. Thank you.

<https://github.com/williamspiro/HubSpot-Developer-Extension/releases/tag/v1.03-beta-3>

If you're not interested in beta testing but still wish to support the extension ratings and reviews are always appreciated
<@U7SL518D6> pinned a message to this channel.

We've hit 60 current extension users. If you like the extension please rate and review it so others can find it :slightly_smiling_face:  <https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/gebemkdecnlgbcanplbgdpcffpdnfdfo>
